00:14:49.082 --> 00:14:54.234
♪Memory's whispers, dreams or illusion♪

00:14:55.386 --> 00:14:58.458
♪Butterflies climb mountains for love♪

00:14:58.458 --> 00:15:00.794
♪Perish before the flowers♪

00:15:01.306 --> 00:15:06.810
♪You seem so distant,
yet right before my eyes♪

00:15:07.450 --> 00:15:09.626
♪A game of chess, a fate of strife♪

00:15:09.626 --> 00:15:12.858
♪I dream of standing
with you, side by side♪

00:15:13.082 --> 00:15:14.842
♪If you would meet me face to face♪

00:15:14.842 --> 00:15:18.522
♪I'd die without a single regret♪

00:15:18.746 --> 00:15:24.570
♪You're the untouchable star♪

00:15:24.794 --> 00:15:30.522
♪I'm the tiniest speck♪

00:15:30.522 --> 00:15:33.690
♪Through all the tides of love and hate♪

00:15:33.690 --> 00:15:36.602
♪Our eyes met across the mortal world♪

00:15:36.602 --> 00:15:38.810
♪When breezes stirred by my window♪

00:15:38.810 --> 00:15:42.522
♪Cherry blossoms rained in the sky♪

00:15:42.522 --> 00:15:48.666
♪You're the distant star♪

00:15:48.666 --> 00:15:54.458
♪I'm the tiniest speck♪

00:15:54.714 --> 00:15:57.434
♪Spend all my devotion♪

00:15:57.850 --> 00:16:00.538
♪For your tears and embrace♪

00:16:00.538 --> 00:16:02.874
♪I'll brave all the blizzards♪

00:16:02.874 --> 00:16:06.746
♪To walk with you♪